query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q1 s t1 tq1 u1) */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow',
'superuser')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('build-process',
'comma',
'docker-swarm',
'exit',
'google-signin',
'http-proxy',
'ioc-container',
'ioexception',
'kafka-consumer-api',
'video-processing',
'webdav',
'webdriverwait')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 1 AND u1.upvotes <= 100
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND a1.question_id = q1.id group by t1.name;
